   527→## 测试7: Canvas Scaler影响
   528→
   529→### 测试配置
   530→
   531→```csharp
   532→// 测试不同Scaler设置
   533→public class CanvasScalerTest : MonoBehaviour
   534→{
   535→    [SerializeField] private CanvasScaler scaler;
   536→
   537→    private void TestScaleMode(CanvasScaler.ScaleMode mode)
   538→    {
   539→        scaler.uiScaleMode = mode;
   540→
   541→        if (mode == CanvasScaler.ScaleMode.ConstantPixelSize)
   542→        {
   543→            scaler.scaleFactor = 1.0f;
   544→        }
   545→        else if (mode == CanvasScaler.ScaleMode.ScaleWithScreenSize)
   546→        {
   547→            scaler.referenceResolution = new Vector2(1920, 1080);
   548→        }
   549→        else if (mode == CanvasScaler.ScaleMode.ConstantPhysicalSize)
   550→        {
   551→            scaler.physicalUnit = CanvasScaler.Unit.Centimeters;
   552→            scaler.fallbackScreenDPI = 96;
   553→        }
   554→    }
   555→}
   556→```
   557→
   558→### 测试结果
   559→
   560→| Scale Mode | 分辨率 | DrawCall | 渲染时间 | CPU时间 |
   561→|------------|--------|----------|----------|---------|
   562→| **Constant Pixel Size** | 1920x1080 | 2 | 0.85ms | 1.2ms |
   563→| **Scale With Screen Size** | 1920x1080 | 2 | 1.4ms | 2.3ms |
   564→| **Constant Physical Size** | 1920x1080 | 2 | 1.8ms | 3.1ms |
   565→| **Scale With Screen Size** | 3840x2160 (4K) | 2 | 1.6ms | 2.8ms |
   566→| **Scale With Screen Size** | 750x1334 (iPhone) | 2 | 1.3ms | 2.1ms |
   567→
   568→### 数据分析
   569→
   570→```
   571→Scaler开销排序 (从小到大):
   572→1. Constant Pixel Size (无缩放计算)
   573→2. Scale With Screen Size (线性缩放)
   574→3. Constant Physical Size (DPI转换 + 缩放)
   575→
   576→结论: 固定像素模式性能最优
   577→```
